const pieData = [ { name: 'Food Companies', value: 6, color: '#10B981' }, { name: 'IT Companies', value: 4, color: '#3B82F6' }, { name: 'Other', value: 2, color: '#F59E0B' } ]; const handleLogout = () => { logout();
